UID:0e4lorgme2v24ous0i6ur32dc0@google.com
CREATED:20250923T134255Z
DESCRIPTION:The <b>Co-Leadership Hive</b>\, launching September 25 and faci
 litated by City Bureau co-founder <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/harr
 ybacklund" target="_blank"><b><u>Harry Backlund</u></b></a>\, is for member
 s who are co-founders or part of collective\, worker-led newsrooms. This Hi
 ve will focus on navigating shared decision making\, dividing responsibilit
 ies and building durable\, healthy co-leadership structures. It’s for pairs
 \, teams and anyone exploring or currently practicing more democratic newsr
 oom governance.<br><br>Tiny News Collective is inviting you to a scheduled 
 Zoom meeting.<br><br>Topic: Co-Leadership Hive (kickoff meeting)<br>Time: S
 ep 25\, 2025 04:00 PM Eastern Time (US and Canada)<br>Join Zoom Meeting<br>
 <a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/j/82607793557?pwd=D1n7EuFt9UBV5ck2stxvrPa1
