CREATED:20260120T235207Z
DESCRIPTION:Feel Good Fundraising: An Intro to Values-Based Major Giving is
  an energizing\,\npractical webinar for nonprofit folks who want to move do
 nors toward deeper\, more\nmeaningful—and larger—gifts without sacrificing 
 their values. We’ll reframe major gifts\nand one-to-one fundraising as rela
 tional\, ethical\, and human (not awkward or\ntransactional). You’ll learn 
 simple ways to invite donors into conversations about\nimpact\, shared valu
 es\, and what it truly takes to fuel your mission. And here’s the good\nnew
 s: major gifts aren’t just for big organizations with big staffs. Even smal
 l teams and\ngrassroots groups can use values-based\, 1:1 fundraising to bu
 ild real relationships and\nmove more money to mission—with more ease and a
  lot more joy.\n\nStaiger Vitelli Associates (SVA) helps mission-drive orga
 nizations build fundraising\npractices that reflect their values\, strength
 en relationships\, and generate the resources\nthey need for impact. Partne
 rs Laura Vitelli and Sarah Staiger bring decades of nonprofit\nleadership a
 nd fundraising experience and a deep belief that fundraising can be ethical
 \,\nrelational\, and even joyful. Grounded in Community-Centric Fundraising
  principles\, SVA\nworks with organizations of all sizes to strengthen indi
 vidual giving\, grow major gifts\,\nand create fundraising practices that a
 lign with their values and move more money to\nmission.
LAST-MODIFIED:20260122T203101Z
LOCATION:https://us06web.zoom.us/j/81187053324?pwd=8iAGEwA3VXdml9wCFo6aLCfw
 fFM6wD.1
