  Third Cohort</b></b><br><br>Three members from the second cohort will shar
 e a little bit about what they’ve worked on during Tiny Vitals’ coaching pr
 ogram this winter. Each organization set data-based goals around organizati
 onal health\, business growth\, and mission alignment to work on four month
 s with a coach.<br><br>We’ll hear and learn from them about what they disco
 vered\, what they tried\, and where they hope to keep making progress. Ther
 e will be some time at the end for Q&amp\;A\, too!<br><br>All coaches and T
 iny News Collective members are invited to join. It’ll be part demo time\, 
 part celebration\, part experiential learning lab!<br><br><br><br>Tiny News
