DESCRIPTION:<p>Our monthly Collective Call is part collective update and pa
 rt town-hall-style conversation. All members\, staff and TNC board members 
 are invited to attend. They take place over Zoom on the first Wednesday of 
 every month at 1 p.m. AKT / 2 p.m. PT / 4 p.m. CT / 5 p.m. ET.</p><p>TNC st
 aff share updates about work underway with the Collective. We highlight pro
 grams\, new resources and decisions that affect members. Founders are invit
 ed to share updates about their work. This is a space to surface challenges
 \, ask questions and celebrate progress. Together\, we discuss what members
  need and explore ways TNC can support them. The goal is to learn from one 
 another and stay connected as a community.</p><br>Tiny News Collective is i
 nviting you to a scheduled Zoom meeting.<br><br>Topic: TNC Collective Call<
 br>Time: This is a recurring meeting Meet anytime<br>Join Zoom Meeting<br><
 a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/j/92829491964?pwd=Sm1oYW9KYmFPWGJFVW1UN3Y1T
