DTSTART:20260223T200000Z
DTEND:20260223T210000Z
DTSTAMP:20260313T190032Z
UID:46roignggb76p4lft3kfp0st5h@google.com
CREATED:20260219T194436Z
DESCRIPTION:If you are fiscally sponsored by Tiny News Collective\, you're 
 invited to a workshop at 3 p.m. ET Monday to walk through our new <a href="
 https://members.tinynewsco.org/r/e07d6d4d?m=0bfdd1a4-76c0-4229-9dbe-c29ecc5
 38e9e" target="_blank">Fiscal Sponsorship Tutorial</a>\, available in the m
 ember portal website.<br><br>This tutorial is a series of articles\, tip sh
 eets and step-by-step guides on all things fiscal sponsorship. In this guid
 e\, we’ve tried to:<ul><li>Reduce the amount of jargon and legalese in favo
 r of clear\, accessible language</li><li>Break a large amount of content do
 wn into bite-sized articles that you can revisit whenever you need a refres
 her on a particular topic</li><li>Balance nitty gritty instructions with th
 e “why” of our fiscal sponsorship processes when possible</li></ul><br>This
  walkthrough will include introductions to:<ul><li>Our new-ish <a href="htt
 ps://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/16gqt58-cw6nAtydBUrP6d9iWf-4gNAFGpQKOtc
 -h8Xs/edit?usp=sharing" target="_blank">Disbursement Request Cover Sheet Te
 mplate</a></li><li>Our new <a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/
 1018BXg7fYEW8qiFyFKgA7st8em9IbSXLdVUOHzN82L0/edit?usp=sharing" target="_bla
 nk">Project Grant Application Budget Template</a></li><li>Our <a href="http
