CREATED:20260220T124129Z
DESCRIPTION:<p><strong>Audience Scoping and Goal Setting: A 60-Minute Works
 hop</strong><br><em>Facilitated by Amanda Zamora</em></p><p>How clearly hav
 e you defined your audience — and are your growth goals actually aligned wi
 th them?</p><p>In this interactive 60-minute workshop\, Amanda Zamora guide
 s participants through a strategic “zoom out” exercise to examine how they 
 are currently defining and scoping their audience\, and why that clarity ma
 tters. Many news organizations and startups struggle with fuzzy audience de
 finitions\, vanity growth metrics\, or goals that don’t reflect real commun
 ity needs. This session helps teams step back and assess whether their assu
 mptions match reality.<br><br>Tiny News Collective is inviting you to a sch
 eduled Zoom meeting.<br><br>Topic: Audience Scoping and Goal Setting: A 60-
 Minute Workshop<br>Time: Feb 23\, 2026 04:00 PM Eastern Time (US and Canada
 )<br>Join Zoom Meeting<br><a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/j/83788891094?pw
 d=rFkLjEjNPx4W5J4NVcgZIEJrRa1QHN.1">https://us06web.zoom.us/j/83788891094?p
 wd=rFkLjEjNPx4W5J4NVcgZIEJrRa1QHN.1</a><br><br>Meeting ID: 837 8889 1094<br
 >Passcode: 094249<br><br>---<br><br>One tap mobile<br>+13052241968\,\,83788
 891094#\,\,\,\,*094249# US<br>+13092053325\,\,83788891094#\,\,\,\,*094249# 
 US<br><br>Join instructions<br><a href="https://us06web.zoom.us/meetings/83
 788891094/invitations?signature=pPQtAzEqtk-PB_iIn6aj4Q-Nmd0jiTkNA8CuzwdQq1A
 ">https://us06web.zoom.us/meetings/83788891094/invitations?signature=pPQtAz
 Eqtk-PB_iIn6aj4Q-Nmd0jiTkNA8CuzwdQq1A</a><br><br></p>
