DESCRIPTION:<b>Woohoo! Join us for Lightning Talks from Tiny Vitals' Second
  Cohort ⚡📊 🫁</b><p></p><p>Members from the second cohort will share a lit
 tle bit about what they've worked on during Tiny Vitals' coaching program t
 his fall. Each organization set data-based goals around organizational heal
 th\, business growth\, and mission alignment to work on four months with a 
 coach.</p><p></p><p>We'll hear and learn from them about what they discover
 ed\, what they tried\, and where they hope to keep making progress. There w
 ill be some time at the end for Q&amp\;A\, too! </p><p></p><p>All coaches a
 nd Tiny News Collective members are invited to join. It'll be part demo tim
 e\, part celebration\, part experiential learning lab!</p>
