 urnalists in Santa Fe\, New Mexico. They publish news stories via social me
 dia\, where some of their videos have gone viral for their informative but 
 slightly comedic nature.<b> We are so excited to have Warren take us throug
 h their social media process! </b><br><b><br></b><br><br>Tiny News Collecti
